trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] WorkflowQueueInfo contains information about the state of a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]WorkflowQueueInfo innehåller information om tillståndet för en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to get a collection of WorkflowQueueInfo objects that represents the state of the workflow queues associated with a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan anropa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>att hämta en uppsättning WorkflowQueueInfo objekt som representerar tillståndet för arbetsflödet köer som är kopplade till en arbetsflödesinstans.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the unconsumed items in the workflow queue.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling oanvända objekt i arbetsflödeskö.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> that contains the unconsumed items in the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>som innehåller oanvända objekten i den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref> associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar namnet på den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref> som är associerade med den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that contains the qualified name each activity subscribed to the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling som innehåller det kvalificerade namnet varje aktivitet prenumererar på den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> that contains the qualified name of the each activity subscribed to the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> som innehåller det kvalificerade namnet för varje aktivitet som prenumererar på den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.
